---
title: fcp-sfd-object-processor — Unhappy Paths
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor CDPUploader as CDP Uploader
    participant CallbackAPI as POST /api/v1/callback
    participant Validation as Validation Layer
    participant MetadataService as Metadata Service
    participant MongoDB as MongoDB
    participant OutboxProcessor as Outbox Processor
    participant SNS as AWS SNS
    participant UploaderProxy as POST /api/v1/uploader/initiate
    participant CDPUploaderSvc as CDP Uploader Service
    participant BlobAPI as GET /api/v1/blob
    participant S3 as AWS S3
    actor Client as Authenticated Client

    Note over CDPUploader,MongoDB: ❌ Callback — Joi Schema Validation Failure
    CDPUploader->>CallbackAPI: POST (malformed payload)
    CallbackAPI->>Validation: Joi schema validation
    Validation-->>CallbackAPI: ❌ schema error
    CallbackAPI->>MongoDB: persistValidationFailureStatus()
    CallbackAPI-->>CDPUploader: 201 Validation failure persisted

    Note over CDPUploader,MongoDB: ❌ Callback — Contract Validation Failure
    CDPUploader->>CallbackAPI: POST (uploadStatus ≠ ready)
    CallbackAPI->>Validation: Contract check
    Validation-->>CallbackAPI: ❌ uploadStatus must be ready
    CallbackAPI->>MongoDB: persistValidationFailureStatus()
    CallbackAPI-->>CDPUploader: 201 Validation failure persisted

    Note over CDPUploader,MongoDB: ❌ Callback — Semantic Validation Failure
    CDPUploader->>CallbackAPI: POST (missing checksumSha256)
    CallbackAPI->>Validation: Semantic file checks
    Validation-->>CallbackAPI: ❌ checksumSha256 required
    CallbackAPI->>MongoDB: persistValidationFailureStatus()
    CallbackAPI-->>CDPUploader: 201 Validation failure persisted

    Note over CDPUploader,MongoDB: ❌ Callback — MongoDB Transaction Failure
    CDPUploader->>CallbackAPI: POST (valid payload)
    CallbackAPI->>MetadataService: persistMetadataWithOutbox()
    MetadataService->>MongoDB: withTransaction()
    MongoDB-->>MetadataService: ❌ transaction error (lock/network)
    MetadataService->>MetadataService: session.endSession()
    MetadataService-->>CallbackAPI: throws error
    CallbackAPI-->>CDPUploader: 500 Internal Server Error

    Note over OutboxProcessor,SNS: ❌ Outbox — SNS Partial Failure
    OutboxProcessor->>MongoDB: getProcessableOutboxEntries()
    MongoDB-->>OutboxProcessor: PENDING entries
    OutboxProcessor->>SNS: publishBatch(messages)
    SNS-->>OutboxProcessor: Successful[msg1] + Failed[msg2]
    OutboxProcessor->>MongoDB: msg1 → SENT
    OutboxProcessor->>MongoDB: msg2 → FAILED (retry next poll)

    Note over OutboxProcessor,SNS: ❌ Outbox — SNS Complete Failure
    OutboxProcessor->>SNS: publishBatch(messages)
    SNS-->>OutboxProcessor: ❌ exception (auth/network)
    OutboxProcessor->>OutboxProcessor: log error, reschedule poll

    Note over Client,S3: ❌ Blob — File Not Found
    Client->>BlobAPI: GET /api/v1/blob/{fileId}
    BlobAPI->>MongoDB: getS3ReferenceByFileId()
    MongoDB-->>BlobAPI: ❌ no document found
    BlobAPI-->>Client: 404 Not Found

    Note over Client,S3: ❌ Blob — S3 Unavailable
    Client->>BlobAPI: GET /api/v1/blob/{fileId}
    BlobAPI->>MongoDB: getS3ReferenceByFileId()
    MongoDB-->>BlobAPI: s3Key + s3Bucket
    BlobAPI->>S3: generatePresignedUrl()
    S3-->>BlobAPI: ❌ S3 unavailable
    BlobAPI-->>Client: 500 Internal Server Error

    Note over Client,CDPUploaderSvc: ❌ Uploader Proxy — Timeout
    Client->>UploaderProxy: POST /api/v1/uploader/initiate
    UploaderProxy->>CDPUploaderSvc: fetch /initiate
    CDPUploaderSvc-->>UploaderProxy: ❌ timeout (>30s)
    UploaderProxy-->>Client: 504 Gateway Timeout

    Note over Client,CDPUploaderSvc: ❌ Uploader Proxy — Service Down
    Client->>UploaderProxy: POST /api/v1/uploader/initiate
    UploaderProxy->>CDPUploaderSvc: fetch /initiate
    CDPUploaderSvc-->>UploaderProxy: ❌ connection refused
    UploaderProxy-->>Client: 502 Bad Gateway
